    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a sweet new ride that won't let you down? I'm parting with my trusty car, and let me tell you, it has been absolute gold! It's in really solid shape\u2014super clean on the inside and runs like a dream. I\u2019ve been diligent about maintenance, so it\u2019s totally ready for your next big road trip or just the daily commute. It\u2019s got a few minor signs of being well-loved, but it still looks fantastic and drives even better. I'd love for it to go to a good home, so come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
